Package com.company

Class AddressBook

java.lang.Object
com.company.AddressBook
public class AddressBook
extends java.lang.Object
Since:
2021-02-24 This class represents and contains a possibly ever growing and/or shrinking "list" of AddressEntries. It contains various methods: readFromFile(filename), add(addressEntry), remove(lastName), find(startOf_lastName), list()
Author:
Mamata Polisetty
